Multi level controllers extension - Production ready - CI 3.1.10 compatible
===========================================================================

An extension to the core router class to allow controllers to be in multi-level directories.

Usage
-----

Copy "MY_Router.php" into "application/core" folder.


Notes
-----

This original extension was written by Damien K. but the code appeared to have no home. 


Extra
-----

If you'd like to request changes, report bug fixes, or contact
the developer of this library, please email <orattue[at]toomanytabs.com>


